<HEADLINE>
<P>
RUSH AND 'SHE' 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 We were appalled at the characterization of Rush Limbaugh on the new 
sketch-comedy program "She TV" (ABC). When the character said at the end of his 
segment, "I hate blacks, I hate blacks, I hate blacks," it sickened us. 
</P>
<P>
 Limbaugh has never said that or even implied it in his political opinions. 
</P>
<P>
 Donalda and Harry Alder, Garden Grove 
</P>
</TEXT>
