<HEADLINE>
<P>
STYLE: FALL BEAUTY; MONUMENTAL MAKEUP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 After several seasons of natural looks, makeup is back in town. With sexy, 
aggressive clothes all the rage, faces now call for strong, dramatic makeup. 
Last season's berry lip shades have given way to bolder colors, from blood red 
to hot fuchsia, which are best when finished with a touch of gloss. 
</P>
<P>
 Styled by Barbara Thornburg 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA091194-0060 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 077920 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
September 11, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
