<TEXT>
<P>
 * The other day I realized how nice it is to do without! I mean without the 
noisy rock concerts from the Pacific Amphitheater, which used to shake our 
house, which is slightly more than a mile away -- but right in the sound 
pattern. The silence, not only in the evenings but in the afternoons when they 
would practice, is a delight. How sweet it is! 
</P>
<P>
 MRS. I.B. MERLES 
