psychology, Valley Christian College 
</P>
<P>
 Background: Former director of Zoe Christian Center. Navy veteran. 
</P>
<P>
 Issues: Judy wants to attract more small businesses to Oxnard, delegate 
authority to community groups, and create more youth programs. He also wants to 
give downtown an architectural face lift with a Spanish motif. 
