<P>
ARIZONA IS TOO MUCH FOR NEW MEXICO STATE; NONCONFERENCE: WILDCATS SCORE 31 
FIRST-HALF POINTS, GIVE UP 83 YARDS RUSHING IN 44-0 VICTORY. 
