who could blame him? 
</P>
<P>
 Teams from the Grand Canyon state have made a habit of beating Carder's 
Antelope Valley College football teams. 
</P>
<P>
 Saturday night's season opener was no different as Mesa buried the Marauders, 
36-7, to drop Carder's record to 1-6 against Arizona teams. 
</P>
