with former Soul II Soul member Nelle Hooper on last year's "Debut," are Graham 
Massey of the techno-dance group 808 State, London-based avant-garde ambient 
trio Black Dog and the classical percussionist and harpist who appeared on the 
"Unplugged" session. 
</P>
