Harvey, with whom she dueted on "(I Can't Get No) Satisfaction" at this year's 
Brit Awards ceremony. "We've been flirting around the idea a lot in our 
postcards to each other," Bjork said after a recent invitation-only screening 
of her new long-form video, "Vessel." 
</P>
<P>
